			"body": "Hi @laurent22,\r\n\r\nThanks for the feedback earlier. I’ve updated the implementation based on the review comments:\r\n\r\n• Adjusted the swipe behaviour so that a left-edge swipe always navigates back to the note list.\r\n• Removed the edit/view conditional logic so the gesture matches the expected behaviour.\r\n• Addressed the earlier review comments in `Note.tsx`.\r\n\r\nThe updated changes have now been pushed to the same branch.\r\n\r\nIf you’re okay with the current implementation, could you please reopen the PR for review? I’d be happy to make any additional adjustments if needed.\r\n\r\nThanks again!\r\n",
